item.title: Big Boss
item.description: The man himself Big Boss, real name John,[3] also known as Jack, and formerly known as Naked Snake, Vic Boss[4][5][6], Ishmael, Saladin, or simply Snake, was a renowned special forces operative and mercenary commander. He founded U.S. Army Special Forces Unit FOXHOUND, along with the mercenary company Militaires Sans Frontières, and was one of the founding members of the Patriots. Big Boss later established the military states of Outer Heavenand Zanzibar Land as bases for his companies, in order to realize his ambitions of creating a nation for soldiers.
